# shadcn/ui Components

This project uses [shadcn/ui](https://ui.shadcn.com/) for UI components.

- UI components are located in `components/ui/`.
- To add a new component, use the shadcn/ui CLI: `npx shadcn-ui@latest add [component-name]`
- The theme can be configured in `components/ui/theme-provider.tsx` and `components/ui/theme-toggle-button.tsx`.

